[Name] Pidgin
[Summary] A multi-protocol messaging client and library.
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] Pidgin consists of three parts, LibPurple - the core \
library, Pidgin - the GTK+ UI and Finch - a ncurses based console UI. \
The library supports multiple protocols via modules, including AIM, \
ICQ, Yahoo!, MSN, XMPP (Jabber), IRC, Napster, Gadu-Gadu, Groupwise, \
Sametime, Bonjour and Zephyr. It has many common features found in \
other clients, as well as many unique features. Pidgin is not endorsed \
by or affiliated with AOL, Google, ICQ, MSN or Yahoo!
[Homepage] http://pidgin.im/
